def corre_plot(X_train, X_train_pred, X_test, X_test_pred):
    x=np.linspace(-2,10)
    y=x
    plt.figure(constrained_layout=True)
    plt.subplot(2,2,1)
    plt.title('train correlation')
    plt.scatter(X_train,X_train_pred,alpha=0.02,s=1)
    plt.plot(x,y,color='green')
    plt.subplot(2,2,2)
    plt.title('test correlation')
    plt.scatter(X_test,X_test_pred,alpha=0.02,s=1)
    plt.plot(x,y,color='green')
    plt.subplot(2,2,3)
    plt.title('train correlation narrow')
    plt.scatter(X_train,X_train_pred,alpha=0.02,s=1,c='black')
    plt.xlim(-3,3)
    plt.ylim(-3,3)
    plt.plot(x,y,color='green')
    plt.subplot(2,2,4)
    plt.title('test correlation narrow')
    plt.scatter(X_test,X_test_pred,alpha=0.02,s=1,c='black')
    plt.xlim(-3,3)
    plt.ylim(-3,3)
    plt.plot(x,y,color='green')
    plt.show()

def history_plot(history):
    plt.figure(figsize=(15,5))
    plt.subplot(1,2,1)
    plt.plot(history.history['loss'])
    plt.plot(history.history['val_loss'])
    plt.title('model loss')
    plt.ylabel('loss')
    plt.xlabel('epoch')
    plt.legend(['train','eval'], loc='upper right')
    plt.subplot(1,2,2)
    plt.plot(history.history['categorical_accuracy'])
    plt.plot(history.history['val_categorical_accuracy'])
    plt.title('model accuracy')
    plt.ylabel('Accuracy')
    plt.xlabel('epoch')
    plt.legend(['train','eval'],loc='upper right')
    plt.show()

def plot_feature_importance(df): 
    n_features = len(df)
    df_plot = df.sort_values('importance')
    f_importance_plot = df_plot['importance'].values
    plt.barh(range(n_features), f_importance_plot, align='center')
    cols_plot = df_plot['feature'].values             
    plt.yticks(np.arange(n_features), cols_plot)      
    plt.xlabel('Feature importance')                  
    plt.ylabel('Feature')

def correlation_coefficient(x, y):
    x_mean = np.mean(x)
    y_mean = np.mean(y)
    numerator = np.sum((x - x_mean) * (y - y_mean))
    denominator = np.sqrt(np.sum((x - x_mean) ** 2) * np.sum((y - y_mean) ** 2))
    return numerator / denominator

# ====== 1. labeling ======

def to_soft_labels(y, grand_truth):
    num_classes = grand_truth.shape[1]
    soft_labels = np.zeros((y.size, num_classes))
    for i, label in enumerate(y):
        soft_labels[i,:] = grand_truth[label]
    return soft_labels

label_GC = to_soft_labels(y_xgb, grand_truth=np.array([[1.,0,0],[0,1.,0],[0,0,1.]]))
overlap_w = 0.05
label_SFC = to_soft_labels(y_xgb, grand_truth=np.array([[1.-overlap_w,overlap_w,0],[overlap_w,1.-2*overlap_w,overlap_w],[0,overlap_w,1.-overlap_w]]))


X_train, X_valid, y_train, y_valid, GC_train, GC_valid, SFC_train, SFC_valid = train_test_split(

# ====== 2. custom loss function ======

def make_soft_ce(soft_labels):
    def soft_ce(preds, dtrain):
        num_class = soft_labels.shape[1]
        preds = preds.reshape(-1, num_class)
        probs = softmax(preds, axis=1)
        grad = probs - soft_labels
        hess = probs * (1 - probs)
        return grad.ravel(), hess.ravel()
    return soft_ce



# ====== 3. accuracy ======

def custom_eval_accuracy(preds, dtrain):
    num_class = preds.shape[1]
    preds = preds.reshape(-1, num_class)
    labels = dtrain.get_label().astype(int)
    y_pred = np.argmax(preds, axis=1)
    acc = (y_pred == labels).mean()
    return 'accuracy', acc

# ====== 4. Optuna tuning ======

def objective_GC(trial):
    params = {
        'max_depth': trial.suggest_int('max_depth', 3, 20),
        'learning_rate': trial.suggest_float('learning_rate', 0.001, 0.3),
        'subsample': trial.suggest_float('subsample', 0.6, 1.0),
        'colsample_bytree': trial.suggest_float('colsample_bytree', 0.6, 1.0),
        'num_class': 3,
        'objective': 'multi:softprob',  # dummy loss fun
        'verbosity': 0,
    }

    bst = xgb.train(
        params,
        dtrain_GC,
        num_boost_round=100,
        evals=[(dvalid_GC, "valid")],
        obj=make_soft_ce(GC_train),
        feval=custom_eval_accuracy,
        early_stopping_rounds=10,
        verbose_eval=False
    )

    return bst.best_score  # accuracy

    X_va, y_va = X_xgb[valid_index], y_xgb[valid_index]
    label_GC_tr, label_GC_va = label_GC[train_index], label_GC[valid_index]
    label_SFC_tr, label_SFC_va = label_SFC[train_index], label_SFC[valid_index]
    dtrain = xgb.DMatrix(X_tr,feature_names=feature_names)
    dvalid = xgb.DMatrix(X_va, label=y_va,feature_names=feature_names)
    
    bst_GC_final = xgb.train(
        best_params_GC,
        dtrain,
        num_boost_round=100,
        evals=[(dvalid, "valid")],
        obj=make_soft_ce(label_GC_tr),
        feval=custom_eval_accuracy,
        early_stopping_rounds=10,
    )

    bst_SFC_final = xgb.train(
        best_params_SFC,
        dtrain,
        num_boost_round=100,
        evals=[(dvalid, "valid")],
        obj=make_soft_ce(label_SFC_tr),
        feval=custom_eval_accuracy,
        early_stopping_rounds=10,
    )

    # class probsafter softmax
    probs_GC = bst_GC_final.predict(dvalid)  # shape: (n_samples, num_class)
    probs_SFC = bst_SFC_final.predict(dvalid)  # shape: (n_samples, num_class)

    # class predclass with highest prob
    y_preds_GC = np.argmax(probs_GC, axis=1)
    y_preds_SFC = np.argmax(probs_SFC, axis=1)
    
    acc_GC = accuracy_score(y_va, y_preds_GC)
    acc_SFC = accuracy_score(y_va, y_preds_SFC)

    # gain features
    cols = list(df_20dims.drop('patient number', axis = 1).columns)
    f_importance_GC = pd.DataFrame([bst_GC_final.get_score(importance_type='gain')]).T.to_numpy().ravel()
    f_importance_GC = f_importance_GC / np.sum(f_importance_GC)
    f_importance_SFC = pd.DataFrame([bst_SFC_final.get_score(importance_type='gain')]).T.to_numpy().ravel()
    f_importance_SFC = f_importance_SFC / np.sum(f_importance_SFC)
    # after - before gain
    df_importance_subtracted = f_importance_SFC - f_importance_GC
    df_importance_subtracted = df_importance_subtracted / np.sum(np.abs(df_importance_subtracted))
    df_importance_subtracted = pd.DataFrame({'feature':feature_names , 'importance':df_importance_subtracted})
    
    df_acc.at['GC',CV_names[nfold]] = acc_GC
    df_acc.at['SFC',CV_names[nfold]] = acc_SFC
    df_importance_GC[CV_names[nfold]] = f_importance_SFC
    df_importance_SFC[CV_names[nfold]] = f_importance_SFC
    df_importance_Diff[CV_names[nfold]] = f_importance_SFC - f_importance_GC
